    {
      "id": "M02",
      "category": "missing_info",
      "description": "模糊時間描述（「最近」）：Agent 應詢問具體日期範圍，不得自行假設",
      "conversationHistory": [],
      "userInput": "有沒有適合 9 歲的活動，最近的",
      "mockApiResponses": {},
      "expectedToolCalls": [],
